                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>Karna<strong> </strong><strong>A</strong><strong>l</strong><strong>l</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>h</strong><strong> </strong><strong>m</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>h</strong><strong>a</strong><strong> </strong><strong>p</strong><strong>e</strong><strong>m</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>f</strong><strong>,</strong><strong>d</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>n</strong><strong> </strong><strong>m</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>h</strong><strong>a</strong><strong> </strong><strong>p</strong><strong>e</strong><strong>m</strong><strong>u</strong><strong>r</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>h</strong></p><p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>karna kita harus memaafkan satu sama lain.</p><p><strong>Penjelasan:</strong></p><p>mengapa kita harus memaafkan satu sama lain?</p><p>karena tidak ada manusia sempurna didunia ini.</p><p></p><br />
